<div class="wpd-comment-text">
<p>@heavy<br />
The problem is you DON&#8217;T THINK!<br />
The issue is, even in situations of extreme natural disasters if what wasl CONSTRUCTED was indeed &#8216;HEAVY DUTY&#8217; structure it usually withstands the forces of nature thereby minimising damage or indeed loss of lives. That&#8217;s some strong structure become temporary shelters disaster management centre points.<br />
But with FAKE DPP infrastructures ndi izi mvula isavumbe, zingokokoloka ngati nyumba yozira.</p>
</div>
